query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `paper_trades` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `accountId` int NOT NULL,
  `positionId` int,
  `strategyId` int,
  `symbol` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `side` enum('BUY','SELL') NOT NULL,
  `quantity` int NOT NULL,
  `price` int NOT NULL,
  `orderType` enum('MARKET','LIMIT','STOP') NOT NULL,
  `pnl` int DEFAULT 0,
  `commission` int DEFAULT 0,
  `executedAt` datetime NOT NULL,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `paper_trades_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`),
  INDEX `idx_paper_trades_account` (`accountId`),
  INDEX `idx_paper_trades_position` (`positionId`),
  INDEX `idx_paper_trades_executed` (`executedAt`)
);
